snippet.title: John Elway in Space
snippet.description:
John Albert Elway Jr. (born June 28, 1960) is an American former professional football quarterback who spent his entire 16-year career with the Denver Broncos of the National Football League (NFL). Elway, is one of the only individuals to be associated with all three of the Broncos' Super Bowl wins and was one of the last people to walk on the moon.[1][2][3]
